[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0031","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0031.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0377","title":"Oracle Solaris INETD 进程表拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Unix 系统存在进程表攻击漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发起大量网络服务连接请求，耗尽系统进程表资源，导致系统无法接受新的连接请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可实施攻击，影响各类 Unix 操作系统。攻击者只需建立大量并发连接即可触发，属于典型的资源耗尽型拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0377"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.993","remediation":"建议将 inetd 替换为 xinetd，并在配置中添加连接速率限制，如 `cps = 25 30` 和 `per_source = 5`；同时通过 `/etc/system` 或 `ulimit` 调大系统进程表上限（如 `max_nprocs`），并使用 TCP Wrappers（`/etc/hosts.allow`）限制仅允许可信来源 IP 连接网络服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securitytracker.com/id/1033881","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0377","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0377.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w9p9-j3v6-q4vf/GHSA-w9p9-j3v6-q4vf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0377.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x78000/77236/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000542.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0031.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0997","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0997.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1168","title":"ISS Internet Security Scanner 5.3 安装脚本本地文件权限提升漏洞","description":"适用于 Linux 平台的 Internet Security Scanner (ISS) 5.3 版本的 install.iss 安装脚本在处理临时文件时存在不安全操作缺陷，未对临时文件路径进行充分校验。本地攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击将临时文件链接至目标系统文件，从而在安装过程中修改任意文件权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 ISS 5.3 for Linux 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1168"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.903","remediation":"安装前手动删除临时文件 `/tmp/iss.install` 并检查是否为符号链接；修改 install.iss 脚本使用 `mktemp` 创建临时文件，避免使用可预测路径；以非 root 用户执行安装程序，降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12640"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0997.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1024","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1024.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1255","title":"Hyperseek 远程配置修改漏洞","description":"Hyperseek 是一款搜索引擎软件，其 admin.cgi 管理接口存在未授权访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接调用 admin.cgi 并传入 edit_file 参数，从而修改 Hyperseek 的配置文件，导致搜索结果劫持、恶意重定向或服务异常。该漏洞利用方式简单，危害中等，CVSS 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1255"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.930","remediation":"Hyperseek 是一款已停止维护的软件（自 1999 年后无更新），admin.cgi 未做任何身份验证即可被远程调用。建议以下措施：①在 Web 服务器层（Apache .htaccess 或 Nginx 配置）为 /cgi-bin/admin.cgi 路径添加 HTTP 基本认证，限制仅授权用户可访问；②在防火墙上限制源 IP，仅允许管理网段访问该脚本路径；③由于厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至活跃维护的替代搜索方案（如 Apache Solr 或 Elasticsearch）以消除长期风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.rootshell.com/archive-j457nxiqi3gq59dv/199902/hyperseek.txt.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1914","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1255","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1255.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5hp3-5xjh-3v56/GHSA-5hp3-5xjh-3v56.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87851/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1255.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1024.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0941","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0941.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1101","title":"Kabsoftware Lydia 弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Kabsoftware Lydia 工具使用弱加密算法将用户密码存储在 lydia.ini 配置文件中，本地攻击者可通过直接读取该配置文件并利用加密算法的弱点轻易解密出明文密码，从而获取系统提升权限。该漏洞属于本地提权类型，攻击者需要具有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议厂商采用强加密算法存储敏感凭据。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1101"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.450","remediation":"由于该软件发行于 1999 年、厂商已停止维护，建议立即迁移至支持强加密（如 AES-256-GCM 或 bcrypt）的现代密码管理工具。如暂时无法替换，可通过文件系统 ACL 将 lydia.ini 的访问权限收紧为仅管理员可读（chmod 600 lydia.ini），同时对所在目录启用操作系统级加密（如 Windows EFS / BitLocker 或 Linux eCryptfs），限制本地低权限用户读取该文件，降低凭据泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12618","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1101","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1101.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fj6p-4jfw-5336/GHSA-fj6p-4jfw-5336.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88477/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1101.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000535.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0941.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0158","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0158.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0485","title":"OpenBSD 2.4 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 内核的 IP 输入处理函数 ipintr() 中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 IP 数据包触发该漏洞，导致系统内核崩溃。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.4 版本，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，攻击复杂度较高，攻击者无需认证即可远程实施拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0485"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.883","remediation":"升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 及以上版本已修复该问题。如在受旧版本约束无法升级的遗留系统中，可通过 pf 防火墙对源 IP 进行速率限制（如 `max-src-states` 和 `max-src-conn-rate`），以及在内核配置中禁用 `options IPQUEUE` 支持来缓解拒绝服务攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0158.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0125","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0125.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0460","title":"Linux Kernel autofs 模块缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux autofs 模块存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 autofs 传递超长目录名触发该漏洞，导致目标系统崩溃从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1/2.2 版本，需要本地用户身份才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0460"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.563","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.2.13 或更高版本，该版本在 autofs 模块中添加了目录名长度边界检查，防止缓冲区溢出。如无法升级内核，可通过移除 autofs 内核模块（rmmod autofs）或限制本地用户对 autofs 挂载点的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/312","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19250"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0125.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0406","title":"Digital Unix Networker nsralist 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Digital Unix（Tru64 UNIX）操作系统中 Networker 备份管理工具的 nsralist 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向该程序发送特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构，成功利用后可获取 root 权限，完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Digital Unix 多个版本，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0406"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.760","remediation":"建议升级 Digital Unix 至 4.0F 及以上版本，或安装 Compaq 针对 nsralist 缓冲区溢出漏洞发布的 Tru64 UNIX 安全补丁 (SSRT-1999-01)。作为缓解措施，使用 chmod 700 限制 nsralist 二进制文件仅允许 root 执行，并从本地用户中移除对 Networker 程序组的非必要成员权限，同时通过 ACL 限制受影响服务的交互式登录用户范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0406"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0913","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1060","title":"Tetrix TetriNet 守护进程缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Tetrix TetriNet 后台守护进程 1.13.16 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过连接该服务监听的 31457 端口，并提供一个超长的 DNS 主机名触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 TetriNet 1.13.16 及可能更早的版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1060"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.310","remediation":"升级 tetrinetx 到已应用补丁的版本（>1.13.16），或将 UHOSTLEN 从 30 改为 256，将 main.c 中栈缓冲区从 121 改为 UHOSTLEN，并将 net.c 中的 strcpy 替换为 strncpy。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 TCP 31457 端口的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91937090211855&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/340","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1060","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a35e01f-9c82-4365-a727-7af8d726e1c6.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000529.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0913.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1003","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1180","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e 及 Website Pro 2.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 args.cmd 或 args.bat 参数传递 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号等）执行任意系统命令。由于服务器未对用户输入做有效过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害较大。该漏洞影响 O'Reilly 系列 Web 服务器产品。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1180"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.360","remediation":"O'Reilly WebSite 1.1e/Website Pro 2.0 已停止维护，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx），并彻底停止使用旧版软件。如无法立即迁移，可在 Web 服务器前端部署 WAF 规则拦截包含 shell 元字符（如 `;`、`|`、`&`、反引号）的请求，并对 `args.cmd`、`args.bat` 参数输入进行严格白名单过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/buffer.html","http://www.tryc.on.ca/archives/bugtraq/1999_1/0612.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1180","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1180.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/args_bat.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j/GHSA-q697-gcxw-q87j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88632/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1180.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000527.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/args_bat.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1003.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1003.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0026","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0374","title":"Debian GNU/Linux cfengine 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 发行版中的 cfengine 软件包存在符号链接攻击漏洞。cfengine 是一款基于主机的配置管理工具，通常以 root 权限运行。由于其在处理临时文件时未充分验证符号链接的真实性，拥有本地账户权限的攻击者可通过在可写目录中创建恶意符号链接（指向 /etc/shadow 等系统关键文件），诱导 cfengine 以 root 权限错误地读取或覆写目标文件，导致敏感信息泄露或系统完整性破坏。该漏洞利用条件为攻击者需具备本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0374"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.563","remediation":"建议升级 cfengine 至 1.5.4 及以上版本，该版本修复了临时文件创建中的符号链接跟随漏洞。使用 cfengine 管理文件时避免将临时文件写入公共可写目录（如 /tmp），或使用专属临时目录并设置 umask 077 限制访问权限。在 Debian 系统中及时应用 apt-get update && apt-get upgrade 保持软件包更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0374"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0026.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1027","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1260","title":"Hughes Technologies mSQL 信息泄露漏洞","description":"mSQL（Mini SQL）2.0.6 版本存在信息泄露漏洞。攻击者可通过发送 ServerStats 查询请求，未经验证的远程用户即可获取服务器的敏感信息，包括当前在线用户列表、数据库名称以及服务器版本等关键数据。该漏洞源于 mSQL 2.0.6 对 ServerStats 查询的权限验证不足，导致攻击者能够轻易提取数据库服务器的详细配置信息和运行状态，对数据库系统的安全性和隐私性造成严重威胁。该漏洞可通过简单的网络请求触发，无需任何特殊权限即可执行，从而为攻击者提供了大量关于目标系统内部结构的敏感信息，有可能进一步为后续攻击行动提供支持。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1260"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.557","remediation":"升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。升级到 mSQL 2.0.6 以上版本，以获取漏洞修复，或禁用 ServerStats 查询功能以防止信息泄露，建议部署权限控制和认证机制限制对查询功能的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91910115718150&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1777","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1260","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c/GHSA-7fw7-4m2q-jp4c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87764/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1260.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e2ff807e9fd18d30d388cc2c559c111ff993a143/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1027.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0311","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0714","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX edauth 命令漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 操作系统的 edauth 认证管理命令存在信息泄露漏洞。该命令在处理认证数据库时权限控制不当，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞越权读取敏感数据，导致部分机密信息泄露。攻击者需具备系统本地访问权限，攻击复杂度低，无需额外认证即可触发。CVSS v2 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0714"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.203","remediation":"建议立即安装 Compaq 发布的 Tru64 UNIX 安全补丁包（如 SSRT-1999 相关补丁），具体版本请查阅 Digital/Compaq Security Advisory 对应发行版。如无法升级，应移除 edauth 命令的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/edauth），并限制仅授权管理员可通过 wheel 组执行。长期建议迁移至受支持的操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0714"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0311.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0043","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0404","title":"SmartMax MailMax SMTP 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 的 SMTP 服务组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统 SMTP 端口发送特制的超长请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台下的 MailMax SMTP 服务器 1.0 版本，攻击复杂度低，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0404"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.490","remediation":"SmartMax MailMax 1.0 已停止维护，官方不再提供安全补丁。建议立即升级或迁移至仍在积极维护的邮件服务器，如 hMailServer、MailEnable 或 Windows Server SMTP 服务。如无法立即迁移，应在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 SMTP 端口（TCP 25），并部署入侵检测系统监控异常 SMTP 流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0404","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20600"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0043.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0612","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0372","title":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 安装程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"BackOffice Server 安装程序在安装过程中会将账户名和密码以明文形式写入 reboot.ini 配置文件中，安装完成后未自动删除该文件，导致敏感信息泄露。本地攻击者可通过读取该文件获取系统账户凭据，进而提升权限或进行横向移动。该漏洞影响 Microsoft BackOffice Server 相关版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击者需具备本地文件读取权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0372"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.307","remediation":"安装 BackOffice Server 4.0 完成后，立即手动删除 `<系统盘>:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini` 文件，该文件包含 SQL Executive、Exchange Services 和 MTS Remote Administration 账户的明文密码。无论安装成功或失败，均须执行删除操作。删除后该文件不会自动重建，除非重新安装 BackOffice 4.0。同时建议限制本地登录权限，仅允许管理员访问服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ217004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-005","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19192","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0372.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0372","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0372.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gcm6-ww8r-qm6x/GHSA-gcm6-ww8r-qm6x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0611","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0371","title":"Lynx lynx 本地符号链接敏感文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Lynx 文本浏览器在处理临时文件时存在不安全的符号链接跟踪漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 /tmp 目录下预创建指向目标敏感文件的符号链接，诱导 Lynx 将临时数据写入该链接指向的文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件，导致数据破坏或权限提升。利用条件为攻击者拥有本地账户权限且 Lynx 以当前用户权限运行。该漏洞影响早期版本 Lynx，CVSS 评分 1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0371"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.167","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.7.1 或更高版本，该版本已改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免预测 /tmp 路径导致的竞争条件。如无法升级，确保 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod 1777 /tmp），并通过设置环境变量 TMPDIR 指向用户私有临时目录来缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0371"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml"}]